@startuml
title InsightsRadar v1 - Manual Backfill Flow

actor Operator
participant "Worker API\nPOST /api/admin/backfill" as API
participant "Cloudflare Blog RSS" as RSS
queue "Cloudflare Queue" as Q
participant "Worker Queue Consumer" as Digest
database "D1 Metadata DB" as D1

Operator -> API: POST /api/admin/backfill\n{start_date}
alt invalid or missing token
  API --> Operator: 401 Unauthorized
else invalid start_date
  API --> Operator: 400 Bad Request
else accepted
  API -> RSS: fetch feed
  RSS --> API: feed items
  API -> API: filter eligible by start_date + mode
  API -> API: dedupe canonical URLs
  loop per eligible URL
    API -> Q: enqueue {canonicalUrl, reason=manual_backfill}
  end
  API --> Operator: 200 {enqueued:n}
end

Q -> Digest: deliver jobs
Digest -> D1: read article + keywords
Digest -> D1: terminal state updates\n(processed or digest_failed)

@enduml
